title: Flashback to The Migos interview and more
itunes:title: Flashback to The Migos interview and more
description:
Today on the show we flashed back to the time we gave the Migos their flowers for their hardwork and consistency in the music game, as they also celebrated their new album coming out. Also, we flashed back to when Charalamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Ronnie O'Neal the man that represented himself in court and fabricating evidence about killing his family members. We also flashed back to some unforgettable questions our listeners asked during "Ask Yee" and "Ask C &E"
